Galleria,is,a,JavaScript,image,gallery,framework,that,allows,users,to,create,and,manage,web,and,mobile,image,galleries,Galleria,offers,different,themes,for,different,design,looks,of,galleries,The,Galleria,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Galleria,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,playing,slideshows,managing,images,and,editing,images